  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients participate in Buried in Treasures Workshop (BIT) that has been shown to improve
      symptoms of hoarding disorder. To target levels of clutter, the investigators are testing an
      intervention to add in-home decluttering practice to the BIT workshop.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
