  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years or older at consent

          -  Primary hoarding disorder, Saving Inventory Revised greater than or equal to 40.

          -  Clutter Image Rating Scale greater than or equal to 3 and less than or equal to 7.

          -  Low risk for eviction

          -  English speaking

          -  Will and able to understand and complete consent procedures

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hoarding disorder not primary

          -  Severely depressed individuals; Hamilton Depressions Rating Scale greater than 30 or
             judged clinically to be at risk of suicide with Columbia Suicide Severity Scale

          -  Unable or unwilling to allow study staff into home for home assessment OR a Clutter
             Image Rating Score of less than 2 or greater than 7.

          -  At risk for eviction

          -  Animal Hoarding or squalor of any kind
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
